      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. She\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really wonderful shape! I\u2019ve taken great care of her, and she runs smoothly, making every trip a total breeze. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that looks great and feels even better on the road, this is the one for you. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and see just how well she's been loved!",
