    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering the precise turn-in and balanced weight distribution this chassis is renowned for. Though it exhibits minor cosmetic wear consistent with an enthusiast-driven life, the drivetrain remains potent with linear power delivery and an urgent exhaust note. A true driver\u2019s specification for those who value mechanical transparency and analog feedback.",
